    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HER TREES : PUZZLE DREAM</strong> 是一款独特的点击解谜游戏，您可以移动和组合物体来解决难题。揭开隐藏在梦中的奇异谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是系列的第三部作品，但新玩家也可以作为独立的游戏来享受。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300800/extras/a1029a2acf7d42e061f3c3c06f4c2656.poster.avif?t=1771280208\" width=430 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300800/extras/a1029a2acf7d42e061f3c3c06f4c2656.webm?t=1771280208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300800/extras/a1029a2acf7d42e061f3c3c06f4c2656.mp4?t=1771280208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过 40 个独特的难题</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以通过直觉和观察来解决的难题，无需繁琐的计算或记录</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提示和答案在一定时间后可用</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏时长约为 1.5-3 小时</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>适合多种玩家：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >非语言游戏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完全黑白设计，难题可以不受色彩感知的影响而解决</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不含依赖声音的难题</p></li></ul>",
